---
// Contact Section - Formulario y datos de contacto
---

<section id="contacto" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-pfc-black mb-4">
        Agenda la clase <span class="text-pfc-red">gratuita</span> de tu hijo
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-pfc-gray">
        Déjanos tus datos y uno de nuestros coordinadores deportivos te contactará en menos de 24 horas con horarios, tarifas y cupos disponibles.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] gap-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-pfc-gray-light rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-10">
        <form
          action="https://formsubmit.co/promesasfcmanizales@gmail.com"
          method="POST"
          class="grid gap-6"
          aria-labelledby="contact-form-title"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Nueva solicitud desde landing Promesas FC" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
          <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table" />

          <h3 id="contact-form-title" class="text-2xl font-semibold text-pfc-black">
            Cuéntanos sobre tu deportista
          </h3>

          <div>
            <label for="parent-name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-pfc-black mb-2">Nombre del acudiente</label>
            <input
              id="parent-name"
              name="Nombre del acudiente"
              type="text"
              required
              autocomplete="name"
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-transparent focus:border-pfc-red focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pfc-red/40 px-4 py-3 bg-white text-pfc-black"
              placeholder="Ej. Laura Gómez"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <label for="child-age" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-pfc-black mb-2">Edad del deportista</label>
              <input
                id="child-age"
                name="Edad del deportista"
                type="number"
                min="3"
                max="15"
                required
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-transparent focus:border-pfc-red focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pfc-red/40 px-4 py-3 bg-white text-pfc-black"
                placeholder="Ej. 8"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-pfc-black mb-2">Teléfono / WhatsApp</label>
              <input
                id="phone"
                name="Teléfono"
                type="tel"
                required
                autocomplete="tel"
                class="w-full rounded-xl border border-transparent focus:border-pfc-red focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pfc-red/40 px-4 py-3 bg-white text-pfc-black"
                placeholder="Ej. 302 515 0090"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-pfc-black mb-2">Correo electrónico</label>
            <input
              id="email"
              name="Correo"
              type="email"
              required
              autocomplete="email"
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-transparent focus:border-pfc-red focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pfc-red/40 px-4 py-3 bg-white text-pfc-black"
              placeholder="Ej. familia@correo.com"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-pfc-black mb-2">Cuéntanos tus objetivos</label>
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="Mensaje"
              rows="4"
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-transparent focus:border-pfc-red focus:ring-2 focus:ring-pfc-red/40 px-4 py-3 bg-white text-pfc-black"
              placeholder="Ej. Buscamos mejorar su técnica y socializar con otros niños"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <label class="inline-flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-pfc-gray">
            <input type="checkbox" name="Autorización de datos" value="Aceptado" required class="mt-1 rounded border-pfc-gray" />
            <span>Autorizo el tratamiento de datos según la Ley 1581 de 2012 para recibir información académica y comercial.</span>
          </label>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-pfc-red text-white font-semibold text-lg px-6 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-red-600 transition-all"
          >
            Enviar solicitud
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <aside class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-pfc-black text-white rounded-3xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Horarios y canales</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/80">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-white">Sede de entrenamiento</p>
                <p>Unidad Deportiva Palogrande · Manizales</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-white">Atención telefónica</p>
                <p>Lunes a viernes 3:00 p.m. - 7:00 p.m.</p>
                <p>Sábados 9:00 a.m. - 12:00 p.m.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pfc-red mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2m-4 8a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V8a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 002-2V2" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-white">Modalidades de pago</p>
                <p>Transferencia, tarjeta débito/crédito, convenios empresariales.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl h-full">
          <iframe
            title="Mapa Promesas Fútbol Club Manizales"
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3977.909897820666!2d-75.49338482526198!3d5.058400938954818!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x8e476ff4f4e6f1a9%3A0xe1ad4806a4efc2fa!2sEstadio%20Palogrande!5e0!3m2!1ses!2sco!4v1700000000000!5m2!1ses!2sco"
            width="100%"
            height="320"
            loading="lazy"
            allowfullscreen=""
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
            class="w-full h-full"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
